interpretation: The "person biking" card is a symbol of movement and progress. It suggests that you are actively pursuing your goals and making strides towards your destination. This card represents the need for a healthy balance of physical activity and mental clarity. It's important to stay motivated and focused on your journey, even if it may be challenging at times. This card also suggests that you are independent and self-reliant, able to navigate your path with confidence. Keep pushing forward and stay disciplined in your pursuits, and you will see the results of your hard work.
